<db:section xml:id="blurRadius-prop">
<db:title>blurRadius : qreal</db:title>
<db:para>This property holds the blur radius in pixels of the drop shadow.</db:para>
<db:para>Using a smaller radius results in a sharper shadow, whereas using a bigger radius results in a more blurred shadow.</db:para>
<db:para>By default, the blur radius is 1 pixel.</db:para>
